---
title: Double Aromatic Chilli & Garlic Prawns with Apple Slaw, Crispy Shallots & Sesame Dressing
description: Fresh prawns are popping with garlic and chilli, spiced to your liking, in this bowl of sesame drizzled slaw to balance it out. To
make dinner really standout, sprinkle over crispy shallots for a tasty crunch.

